\subsection{Contexts}
\begin{itemize}
\item |Q|, context for a sequence of equations in a block.
  Note that the hole can contain a single equation, no equations, or many equations.
\item |QC|, context for a sequence of equations in a block, but with all equations on the left being choice free.
\item |V|, context for a sequence of variables quantified variables in a block.
  Note that the hole can contain a single variable, no variables, or many variables.
\item |SX|, context where choices can be made.
\end{itemize}


